    "description": "The Showtec Cameleon PixelBar 15 Q6 Tour is a powerful 15x 10 watt LED Bar with individually controllable LED pixels, silent, fanless operations and IP65 rating, suitable for indoor and temporary outdoor applications. It has a 33° fixed horizontal and 22° vertical beam angle and features 0-100 % dimmer and 0-15 Hz strobe effects, perfectly suitable for colour mixing on stage. The Cameleon PixelBar 15 Q6 Tour can be controlled manually, via DMX, IR remote, and Master/Slave in either Manual or Auto run mode with many available built-in programs. It is equipped with Seetronic Power Pro True IP65-rated power connectors, which are compatible with the leading brands.",
